title: Strawberry Parfait By Vapetasia
description: Parfait Strawberry delivers the deliciousness of fresh cut strawberries and honey granola clusters layered with sweet and creamy yogurt. A smooth whole-milk yogurt is whipped with vanilla to provide the perfectly balanced mellow creamy flavor. From that base we delicately layer granola clusters kissed with honey and fresh cut strawberries burst with juicy goodness.
